<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
	<meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
	</head>

	<body>
		<h1>You got a new message!</h1>
		<hr>
		<p>You have received a message from <strong><%=@sender.first_name%> <%=@sender.last_name%> </strong>for your listing <strong><%=@listing.name%></strong>.</p> 

		<p>
		Message from <%=@sender.first_name%>:
		<br>
		<em><%=@message%></em>
		<br>
		<p>Respond to the user in one of the following ways:</p>
		<ul>
		<li>Email: <%=@sender.email%></li>
		<li>Phone: <%=@sender.phone%>
		</ul>

		<p>
		Thank you
		</p>
		Petr Duda<br>
		AirBnB Team
	</body>
</html>